{"tid":2050124,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，身為香港人必需抵制五等分垃圾","createTime":"2020-06-04T02:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T03:09:52.000Z","uid":182935,"like":19,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f80fe1e0b23de79e62acb5c429ddaf2270d21860","tid":2050124,"uid":182935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"五等分入面選另一半，表面上好似有五個俾你揀，但實際上五個只有一啲細節唔同，個樣同身材完全一撚樣，根本同工廠倒模出嚟一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，即係冇撚得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似支共要香港人選佢哋俾嘅垃圾做特首一樣，表面有得揀，實際冇得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以作為香港人，請抵制呢套政治嚴重不正確嘅垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要真正有得揀，唔撚要倒模垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5b7d65cfd83a509a31f5d3c05d3046d6ff7840","tid":2050124,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3hLGtt0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hLGtt0.png&h=b65ec6c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"346aa3b32580242dd2cf911e003442ab745d4a10","tid":2050124,"uid":182935,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"eb5b7d65cfd83a509a31f5d3c05d3046d6ff7840","tid":2050124,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3hLGtt0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hLGtt0.png&h=b65ec6c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/